      <title>NatWest Markets 称英国低息债券热潮已过度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/uk-s-low-coupon-bond-rush-is-overdone-says-natwest-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国国民西敏寺银行市场部 (NatWest Markets) 称，英国债券市场中为英国富人提供税收减免的利基市场需求面临下滑的风险。]]></description>
